Cd player and ripper with gnome 2 integration
	
goobox is an cd player and ripper for the gnome 2 environment. it follows the
"just works" principle so its interface is beautiful and easy-to-use.

it uses gnome/gtk+ for its user interface, gstreamer framework for cd playing,
and ripping operations, musicbrainz for cd indexing, and gnomevfs to search
album cover images with google.